      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NEVS DREAM (4) added to the impressive sequence of wins last start when she scored by 7 metres over 2190m at this track. Meets a comparable field and she can go right on with the job. MIDNIGHT PIRATE (9) has been a bit hot and cold and that continued last start when he finished third, beaten 4.5 metres, in a nice return to form at this track over 1790m. May just need a bit of luck at some point from this difficult draw. Finds a suitable assignment and will take plenty of beating once more. IM ALRIGHT JACK (5) is worth plenty of thought off a last-start win by a head at this track over 1790m. RONZEL MICKY (7) must be included on the back of some solid recent form, most recently when fifth at this track over 1790m.",
